text: Ya Bashar (; O Bashar) is the 13th album released by Diana Haddad. It was released by Rotana Records in 2014. It was also Haddad's first collaboration with Arabia's biggest record label. == Release information == Region Date Label Format Arabia December 17, 2014 Rotana Records Digital Download == References == Category:2014 albums Category:Arabic-language mass media
title: Ya Bashar
